mirages. Lastly, I discuss the potential for the\nTransiting Exoplanet Survey Satellite to detect refracted light and consider\nnovel science cases enabled by refracted light spectra from the James Webb\nSpace Telescope.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Sep 2017 17:59:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-25"}
