veloped for the flow in the bypass tubes and in the nozzle take\ninto account rarefaction effects and are validated by comparing pressures\npredictions in the RFD chamber with the pressure measurements. The GEVKM is\nverified and validated in the wide range of pressures and absorbed powers of\ndifferent plasma reactors and is used in a parametric investigation of the RFD\nchamber of the HCNHIS with hydrogen inlet flow rates 5-1000 sccm and absorbed\npowers 200-1000 W.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Sep 2017 20:20:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-22"}
